				</li>
				<li>
					<a href="#">
						<i class="fa-regular fa-circle-user"></i>
					</a>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</nav>
	</header>

	<section class="bg-black text-white w-screen h-screen text-center relative overflow-hidden">
		<h1 class="pt-40 text-5xl font-medium">Model 3</h1>
		<p>From $29,740* After Federal Tax Credit & Est. Gas Savings</p>

		<div>
			<button>Order Now</button>
			<button>Demo Drive</button>
		</div>

		<p>*Price before incentives and savings is $40,240, excluding taxes and fees. Subject to change. Learn about est. gas savings.</p>

		<div class="absolute top-0 bottom-0 h-full">
			<video class="object-cover" autoplay muted loop src="/Video.mp4"></video>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
